{
  "stem": "617.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Therefore, every time we arrived to a station, they would just let us sit there, sometimes for hours, before the other trains would pass by, especially military trains, you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we could see a lot of German soldiers in other trains going by.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The doors stayed that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never got off the train, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never got off the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I could remember, I think they were taking off some of the pails from the-- from the wash-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were given new, like, fresh ones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they would just open a little more there and take them out, and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then we arrived to Auschwitz, which we didn't know-- we were, at least I was in my family-- if my parents knew, they didn't say it where we are going or what is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the doors opened-- we arrived at night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It must have been about midnight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All I could see when the doors opened, a lot of fires, like the fires used to-- like so high.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To me it looked like all the way up to the sky, the red-- the red flames.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the smell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Didn't know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Didn't know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like I said, we were very naive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the, the doors were opened and there were these men with striped uniforms and saying, get out, get out, get out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody get out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember we still had a piece of bread which was left over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I stuck it in my pocket to give for my little brother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as we got out of the cars, there again these striped men were saying men to go separately to this side, and women and children to this side.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
